1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,752
=Episode 21=
(The Dark Side of the Moon)

3
00:01:38,898 --> 00:01:41,098
Stop fidgeting or drinking water.

4
00:01:42,137 --> 00:01:43,577
Sit properly.

5
00:01:44,417 --> 00:01:45,368
I have things for you.

6
00:01:51,458 --> 00:01:52,658
This is for you.

7
00:01:57,777 --> 00:02:00,497
You're making such a big fuss
over these crummy gloves,

8
00:02:00,857 --> 00:02:03,057
insisting that we can't have water
after the meal.

9
00:02:04,098 --> 00:02:07,417
Do we have to set off some firecrackers
before putting them on?

10
00:02:07,777 --> 00:02:10,378
Stop nagging.
Give them back if you don't want them.

11
00:02:11,457 --> 00:02:12,897
It's paid by me. So they're mine.

12
00:02:12,897 --> 00:02:14,098
It's my hard-earned money.

13
00:02:14,417 --> 00:02:15,577
It's not paid by you.

14
00:02:17,818 --> 00:02:20,017
It's like when a donkey
grinds beans to make tofu,

15
00:02:20,978 --> 00:02:22,697
it immediately forgets who feeds it.

16
00:02:23,978 --> 00:02:26,978
Besides, you should study properly
instead of having part-time jobs.

17
00:02:28,737 --> 00:02:29,297
Fine.

18
00:02:29,857 --> 00:02:30,818
When I earn money later,

19
00:02:30,818 --> 00:02:32,258
I'll just buy myself some good food.

20
00:02:32,297 --> 00:02:34,378
At least I will enjoy them, right?

21
00:02:34,697 --> 00:02:36,617
Buying things for you is a real waste.

22
00:02:37,538 --> 00:02:38,697
That's quite rhythmic.

23
00:02:40,158 --> 00:02:41,538
Alright, knowing that is enough.

24
00:02:41,538 --> 00:02:42,378
Stop buying things.

25
00:02:42,978 --> 00:02:45,017
Look at all this money spent.
None of it is cheap.

26
00:02:45,417 --> 00:02:46,488
Spend the money on food.

27
00:02:47,297 --> 00:02:48,577
Xiaofei, come here quickly.

28
00:02:48,857 --> 00:02:49,538
Move the table.

29
00:02:50,778 --> 00:02:51,737
We're playing cards.

30
00:02:53,417 --> 00:02:55,378
Oh, my.

31
00:02:55,857 --> 00:02:57,938
Can't our family's leisure activities

32
00:02:57,938 --> 00:02:59,137
be a bit more varied?

33
00:02:59,338 --> 00:03:00,778
Every time it's just cards.

34
00:03:01,258 --> 00:03:02,498
Isn't it monotonous?

35
00:03:02,658 --> 00:03:03,938
You've seen the big world now,

36
00:03:04,697 --> 00:03:05,938
and you find home boring?

37
00:03:08,818 --> 00:03:10,177
Then buy us a TV.

38
00:03:11,658 --> 00:03:12,778
So the atmosphere at home

39
00:03:14,258 --> 00:03:15,538
will be lively and cheerful.

40
00:03:16,098 --> 00:03:17,656
We can watch the Spring Festival Gala,

41
00:03:17,737 --> 00:03:19,098
saving us from doing it ourselves.

42
00:03:19,538 --> 00:03:20,498
A TV is nothing.

43
00:03:20,778 --> 00:03:23,737
Just you wait.
I'll get one for you, okay?

44
00:03:23,857 --> 00:03:24,504
Cut the deck.

45
00:03:27,857 --> 00:03:28,457
You cut.

46
00:03:29,058 --> 00:03:30,417
Don't cut the first card.

47
00:03:32,697 --> 00:03:33,577
You'll get me a TV?

48
00:03:33,577 --> 00:03:35,538
Don't brag and leave yourself an out.

49
00:03:37,338 --> 00:03:41,177
Just work hard
and focus on your studies.

50
00:03:42,498 --> 00:03:43,778
Are you dating anyone?

51
00:03:46,818 --> 00:03:47,417
No.

52
00:03:49,378 --> 00:03:50,417
You're in college now.

53
00:03:50,697 --> 00:03:51,577
If you see a good guy,

54
00:03:51,818 --> 00:03:53,538
you can't be slow about it.

55
00:03:53,818 --> 00:03:55,058
Don't let others take them.

56
00:03:55,938 --> 00:03:57,577
You allow Xiaoming to have a boyfriend?

57
00:04:00,417 --> 00:04:03,498
If she doesn't fish in the college,
where all the big fish gather,

58
00:04:03,818 --> 00:04:06,058
is she supposed to catch one
in the vast ocean later?

59
00:04:06,498 --> 00:04:07,697
Is she even capable?

60
00:04:09,498 --> 00:04:10,058
What about me?

61
00:04:10,778 --> 00:04:12,658
How come I'm not capable?

62
00:04:13,177 --> 00:04:14,697
Lots of people pursue me, okay?

63
00:04:16,737 --> 00:04:18,138
What's gotten into you?

64
00:04:18,538 --> 00:04:20,057
You brag nonstop today.

65
00:04:21,458 --> 00:04:23,778
Listen to me. Dating is okay.

66
00:04:24,377 --> 00:04:27,098
But you're a girl.
You need to protect yourself.

67
00:04:27,778 --> 00:04:30,098
See if fate brings you a good guy,
and then date.

68
00:04:30,497 --> 00:04:31,698
Better none than wrong.

69
00:04:32,138 --> 00:04:33,937
Though I may not have
successful experience,

70
00:04:33,937 --> 00:04:35,018
I've learned from failure.

71
00:04:35,018 --> 00:04:36,098
Alright, alright.

72
00:04:36,497 --> 00:04:37,057
You want it?

73
00:04:37,458 --> 00:04:37,958
Yes.

74
00:04:40,018 --> 00:04:41,497
Xiaoming, did you see Bai Shu?

75
00:04:41,737 --> 00:04:42,237
No.

76
00:04:42,817 --> 00:04:43,512
I won't play.

77
00:04:43,617 --> 00:04:44,857
So boring. Not fun at all.

78
00:04:44,857 --> 00:04:45,458
I'm sleeping.

79
00:04:45,978 --> 00:04:47,177
So annoying.

80
00:04:47,177 --> 00:04:48,824
Will she return for Chinese New Year?

81
00:04:51,497 --> 00:04:52,658
Go get my slippers.

82
00:04:54,458 --> 00:04:54,958
Okay.

83
00:04:56,737 --> 00:04:58,138
We didn't even finish one hand.

84
00:05:00,098 --> 00:05:01,698
Just sleep soundly in broad daylight.

85
00:05:05,057 --> 00:05:06,057
Such a downer.

86
00:05:19,898 --> 00:05:21,817
Come on, sleep well.

87
00:05:47,937 --> 00:05:49,417
Why aren't you coming?

88
00:05:49,417 --> 00:05:51,098
Didn't you want to see Bai Shu?

89
00:05:51,098 --> 00:05:53,538
I've come several times
during winter break!

90
00:05:53,617 --> 00:05:55,497
But she wasn't at school
during winter break.

91
00:05:56,458 --> 00:05:57,338
It's been a year.

92
00:05:58,218 --> 00:06:00,458
Not even a word.
She just doesn't want to see me.

93
00:06:00,737 --> 00:06:02,138
Don't overthink it.

94
00:06:05,057 --> 00:06:06,538
That building there. Dorm 8.

95
00:06:06,677 --> 00:06:07,677
Come on, look.

96
00:06:07,978 --> 00:06:08,497
Let's go.

97
00:06:08,698 --> 00:06:09,458
Are you sure?

98
00:06:17,018 --> 00:06:17,578
Bai Shu.

99
00:06:19,497 --> 00:06:20,417
I need to talk to you.

100
00:06:21,658 --> 00:06:24,617
- Who's this guy?
- I have never seen him before.

101
00:06:26,817 --> 00:06:28,617
We know nothing. How can we find her?

102
00:06:28,937 --> 00:06:30,578
We'll find her if we check every room.

103
00:06:30,778 --> 00:06:33,497
Excuse me, do you know
which dorm room Bai Shu lives in?

104
00:06:33,817 --> 00:06:34,778
- Bai Shu?
- Bai Shu?

105
00:06:35,218 --> 00:06:35,937
- No idea.
- No idea.

106
00:06:35,937 --> 00:06:37,538
Bai Shu hasn't been back for days.

107
00:06:38,257 --> 00:06:40,458
She's with a rich guy now.
Why would she live here?

108
00:06:40,497 --> 00:06:41,778
Don't be silly. Let's go.

109
00:06:41,778 --> 00:06:43,218
What are you doing? Calm down.

110
00:06:43,218 --> 00:06:43,737
Hey.

111
00:06:43,737 --> 00:06:45,417
- What are you doing?
- Why are you stopping me?

112
00:06:45,417 --> 00:06:47,257
Don't cause trouble for Bai Shu.

113
00:06:47,257 --> 00:06:48,898
Just calm down and sit for a bit, okay?

114
00:06:49,297 --> 00:06:51,257
Sit down. Calm yourself.

115
00:06:51,658 --> 00:06:52,158
Sit here.

116
00:06:52,177 --> 00:06:54,578
Even if I calm down,
I still need to find out what happened.

117
00:06:54,737 --> 00:06:55,937
Then ask Bai Shu.

118
00:06:56,057 --> 00:06:57,257
I don't have her phone number.

119
00:07:06,098 --> 00:07:06,737
Shu,

120
00:07:07,778 --> 00:07:08,778
don't ask me anything.

121
00:07:09,458 --> 00:07:10,578
I don't want to explain it.

122
00:07:11,018 --> 00:07:11,898
Then why did you come?

123
00:07:14,057 --> 00:07:15,737
Your translation fee is on this card.

124
00:07:16,297 --> 00:07:17,978
I added an extra 100,000 yuan.

125
00:07:18,898 --> 00:07:20,057
It's all on this card.

126
00:07:20,497 --> 00:07:21,817
This is all I can do.

127
00:07:22,257 --> 00:07:23,538
The password is your birthday.

128
00:07:24,817 --> 00:07:25,617
Shu, take it.

129
00:07:25,857 --> 00:07:26,978
That's not my birthday.

130
00:07:27,658 --> 00:07:28,698
It's the day she died.

131
00:07:29,497 --> 00:07:30,538
You take it. I'm driving.

132
00:07:34,218 --> 00:07:35,057
I deserve this.

133
00:07:36,317 --> 00:07:36,817
Yeah.

134
00:07:36,817 --> 00:07:37,317
Wang Hao,

135
00:07:38,218 --> 00:07:39,737
if you really did something to me,

136
00:07:40,578 --> 00:07:42,578
I would curse you to go to hell.

137
00:07:49,937 --> 00:07:52,338
By the way, your phone
was left at the hotel.

138
00:07:53,018 --> 00:07:54,177
The hotel called me.

139
00:07:54,698 --> 00:07:55,698
I got it back for you.

140
00:07:56,257 --> 00:07:57,098
I don't want it.

141
00:08:07,617 --> 00:08:08,338
Bai Shu's number.

142
00:08:09,898 --> 00:08:10,648
From Zhang Fang?

143
00:08:12,617 --> 00:08:13,377
You two, just wait.

144
00:08:14,698 --> 00:08:16,778
Actually, everyone
has their own reasons.

145
00:08:16,778 --> 00:08:18,297
They might not want to tell others.

146
00:08:19,098 --> 00:08:20,338
You need to relax a bit

147
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:22,698
and give others a chance to relax too.

148
00:08:26,098 --> 00:08:27,098
Ren Xiaoming's call.

149
00:08:28,578 --> 00:08:29,208
Give it to me.

150
00:08:34,897 --> 00:08:35,418
Hello?

151
00:08:35,537 --> 00:08:36,178
It's me.

152
00:08:36,698 --> 00:08:39,017
I came to La City. I'm at your school.

153
00:08:39,377 --> 00:08:40,098
I miss you.

154
00:08:40,737 --> 00:08:41,698
I want to see you.

155
00:08:43,818 --> 00:08:44,698
I'm not at school.

156
00:08:45,377 --> 00:08:46,298
You're not?

157
00:08:49,017 --> 00:08:49,517
It's okay.

158
00:08:49,978 --> 00:08:51,537
Then... then I'll head back first.

159
00:08:51,537 --> 00:08:53,598
We can meet up
when you're free later, okay?

160
00:08:55,617 --> 00:08:56,178
Okay.

161
00:08:57,458 --> 00:08:58,298
Take care.

162
00:09:03,458 --> 00:09:03,958
Bye.

163
00:09:05,257 --> 00:09:05,857
Bye.

164
00:09:17,338 --> 00:09:18,637
She's not here? Let's go.

165
00:09:18,978 --> 00:09:21,037
Come on.
I'll take you for some good food.

166
00:09:21,698 --> 00:09:22,938
What to eat?

167
00:09:24,617 --> 00:09:25,218
Guo Bao Rou.

168
00:09:29,377 --> 00:09:32,698
Guo Bao Rou? Annoying.

169
00:10:16,298 --> 00:10:17,058
Maybe

170
00:10:18,537 --> 00:10:20,617
let's not eat here. It's too expensive.

171
00:10:21,058 --> 00:10:21,558
Yeah.

172
00:10:21,818 --> 00:10:22,318
Let's go.

173
00:10:22,777 --> 00:10:23,418
My treat.

174
00:10:29,137 --> 00:10:29,857
You have money?

175
00:10:31,777 --> 00:10:33,218
I just got some money today.

176
00:10:33,818 --> 00:10:35,058
I want to spend it all.

177
00:10:36,578 --> 00:10:37,377
Who gave it to you?

178
00:10:41,777 --> 00:10:42,458
That guy?

179
00:10:44,578 --> 00:10:45,497
Which guy do you mean?

180
00:10:47,578 --> 00:10:48,728
The guy with the luxury car.

181
00:10:53,777 --> 00:10:54,418
Is it him?

182
00:10:55,818 --> 00:10:56,698
Let's go in.

183
00:11:00,698 --> 00:11:01,218
Let's go.

184
00:11:13,897 --> 00:11:14,397
Sit.

185
00:11:17,058 --> 00:11:18,137
What do you want to eat?

186
00:11:19,657 --> 00:11:20,377
Anything.

187
00:11:22,017 --> 00:11:22,938
You haven't answered.

188
00:11:25,058 --> 00:11:25,897
He gave me the money.

189
00:11:27,578 --> 00:11:29,058
Are you really being his mistress?

190
00:11:33,017 --> 00:11:35,017
Know what the girls
at your school say about you?

191
00:11:36,857 --> 00:11:37,857
What were you thinking?

192
00:11:48,257 --> 00:11:49,418
You two can date?

193
00:11:49,857 --> 00:11:51,377
Don't I have the right to be loved?

194
00:11:53,938 --> 00:11:54,857
I haven't told anyone.

195
00:11:55,137 --> 00:11:56,578
I only told Zhang Fang.

196
00:11:56,857 --> 00:11:58,098
You're disgusting.

197
00:12:09,897 --> 00:12:13,418
I've always aimed for financial freedom
through my own efforts.

198
00:12:13,818 --> 00:12:14,537
Is it disgusting?

199
00:12:14,857 --> 00:12:16,058
Through your own efforts?

200
00:12:17,537 --> 00:12:18,578
You mean being kept?

201
00:12:19,458 --> 00:12:22,098
Being a man's mistress
and sleeping with him?

202
00:12:22,578 --> 00:12:23,617
Is that your effort?

203
00:12:27,537 --> 00:12:28,216
Ren Xiaoming.

204
00:12:29,137 --> 00:12:30,818
You're selling yourself. You know that?

205
00:12:31,818 --> 00:12:32,737
Then what about you?

206
00:12:33,578 --> 00:12:36,248
You made over ten yuan an hour
with that part-time job in Qingzhou.

207
00:12:36,617 --> 00:12:37,978
Wasn't that selling yourself too?

208
00:12:39,537 --> 00:12:40,458
And so cheaply.

209
00:12:59,737 --> 00:13:00,938
What's wrong with you?

210
00:13:03,418 --> 00:13:05,058
Have you been triggered by something?

211
00:13:05,058 --> 00:13:07,298
You weren't like this before.
You've changed.

212
00:13:07,897 --> 00:13:08,938
You can't define me.

213
00:13:10,497 --> 00:13:11,257
Ren Xiaoming,

214
00:13:13,338 --> 00:13:14,617
you're impatient

215
00:13:15,458 --> 00:13:16,458
and self-righteous.

216
00:13:20,257 --> 00:13:21,857
You never see the dark side of the moon.

217
00:13:22,058 --> 00:13:23,818
I don't want to see any moon.

218
00:13:25,058 --> 00:13:26,338
I knew you were lying to me.

219
00:13:26,338 --> 00:13:29,338
You lie and ignore me.
You have no shame.

220
00:13:33,098 --> 00:13:34,178
You're becoming your mom.

221
00:13:34,698 --> 00:13:37,418
I hate it most when people say
I'm like my mom.

222
00:13:45,818 --> 00:13:46,318
Xiaoming.

223
00:13:49,458 --> 00:13:51,537
(Only many years later did I realize)

224
00:13:52,897 --> 00:13:55,537
(what Bai Shu meant
by "the dark side of the moon".)

225
00:13:57,938 --> 00:13:59,698
(If I had known
from the very beginning,)

226
00:14:00,017 --> 00:14:01,938
(I would never have said
those things to her.)

227
00:14:03,818 --> 00:14:05,897
(Instead, I would have spent
a long time)

228
00:14:06,857 --> 00:14:08,137
(on just holding her tightly.)

229
00:14:36,857 --> 00:14:37,657
What's that?

230
00:14:39,818 --> 00:14:42,017
Are you like a cat,
walking without a sound?

231
00:14:43,537 --> 00:14:45,017
Even He Yuqiong has these gloves.

232
00:14:46,338 --> 00:14:47,657
Are these for Ms. Bai Shu?

233
00:14:49,058 --> 00:14:50,058
None of your business.

234
00:14:51,737 --> 00:14:53,017
You leave in two days.

235
00:14:54,338 --> 00:14:55,458
Why not give them to her?

236
00:14:56,338 --> 00:14:57,098
Still talking?

237
00:14:58,777 --> 00:14:59,857
Did you two have a fight?

238
00:15:01,497 --> 00:15:02,257
I'll hit you.

239
00:15:02,537 --> 00:15:03,938
If you don't go find Bai Shu soon,

240
00:15:04,418 --> 00:15:06,418
it'll be another year
before you see her.

241
00:15:08,178 --> 00:15:10,338
I won't go. She doesn't care to see me.

242
00:15:11,938 --> 00:15:13,464
Keeping these gloves won't help you.

243
00:15:13,938 --> 00:15:15,698
Your hands are too big.
You can't wear them.

244
00:15:16,978 --> 00:15:20,058
Fine. Then when I see her,
I'll fling the gloves at her face.

245
00:15:20,257 --> 00:15:21,617
Then we'll forget each other.

246
00:15:23,098 --> 00:15:25,737
If not done now,
there are many things you might regret.

247
00:15:26,857 --> 00:15:29,298
Then I'll pick the gloves up
and fling them at her face again.

248
00:15:29,938 --> 00:15:32,938
Then when you see Ms. Bai Shu,
say hi for me, okay?

249
00:15:38,657 --> 00:15:40,458
Why do you call her Ms. Bai Shu?

250
00:15:41,178 --> 00:15:43,017
But you call He Yuqiong by his name.

251
00:15:43,657 --> 00:15:44,857
I don't like He Yuqiong.

252
00:15:45,178 --> 00:15:46,537
How did he offend you?

253
00:15:48,178 --> 00:15:48,897
He hugged you.

254
00:15:53,338 --> 00:15:55,137
You saw it? When did you see it?

255
00:15:55,418 --> 00:15:56,137
Anything else?

256
00:15:56,458 --> 00:15:57,897
I saw him hug you really tightly.

257
00:16:00,298 --> 00:16:01,938
If you dare tell Mom, I'll kill you.

258
00:16:03,897 --> 00:16:07,298
I won't tell. Then go see Ms. Bai Shu
and say hi for me.

259
00:16:07,938 --> 00:16:09,418
I'll strangle you.

260
00:16:10,617 --> 00:16:11,777
Xiaoming, just go.

261
00:16:19,338 --> 00:16:20,017
Just go.

262
00:16:27,737 --> 00:16:28,497
(Student Dorm 8)
Come out.

263
00:16:32,657 --> 00:16:33,377
Shameless!

264
00:16:33,737 --> 00:16:35,578
I'll slap you dead! You homewrecker!

265
00:16:35,818 --> 00:16:37,698
Come on! Everyone, look!

266
00:16:38,137 --> 00:16:40,058
She is a shameless mistress!

267
00:16:40,178 --> 00:16:42,178
She had a hotel room
with my husband in Wuchuan.

268
00:16:42,338 --> 00:16:44,818
Come on, everyone, look!
Remember her face.

269
00:16:45,657 --> 00:16:48,058
Wretch! I'm talking to you!

270
00:16:48,657 --> 00:16:49,458
Shameless!

271
00:16:49,777 --> 00:16:50,298
Get lost!

272
00:16:51,578 --> 00:16:53,458
Who are you? Who are you cursing?

273
00:16:54,537 --> 00:16:56,137
Who are you cursing? Take that back!

274
00:16:56,777 --> 00:16:58,497
What's it to you?

275
00:16:59,777 --> 00:17:01,137
Don't you dare touch her!

276
00:17:02,298 --> 00:17:04,418
Who are you hitting?
Who said you can hit her?

277
00:17:05,458 --> 00:17:06,337
You dare hit me?

278
00:17:06,658 --> 00:17:07,297
Let go!

279
00:17:07,577 --> 00:17:08,077
Let go!

280
00:17:08,218 --> 00:17:09,138
Bai Shu, go!

281
00:17:09,497 --> 00:17:09,997
Go!

282
00:17:10,577 --> 00:17:11,378
Separate them!

283
00:17:11,898 --> 00:17:12,497
Separate them!

284
00:17:13,010 --> 00:17:13,964
(Security guard)
Let go!

285
00:17:15,017 --> 00:17:15,737
Let go!

286
00:17:18,097 --> 00:17:18,618
Xiaoming!

287
00:17:19,017 --> 00:17:20,218
Let go!

288
00:17:36,257 --> 00:17:39,378
Oh my, that was so cool!

289
00:17:39,978 --> 00:17:41,858
You slapped Zhou Na
right across her face.

290
00:17:41,978 --> 00:17:44,418
It stunned Zhou Na
and stunned me as well.

291
00:17:44,618 --> 00:17:47,017
When did you learn that?
Did you secretly practice at home?

292
00:17:48,297 --> 00:17:49,577
I went wham

293
00:17:49,777 --> 00:17:52,297
and pushed Zhou Na
to the ground from far away.

294
00:17:52,777 --> 00:17:53,537
You know what?

295
00:17:53,537 --> 00:17:55,777
With my strength,
she couldn't get up at all.

296
00:18:03,898 --> 00:18:05,418
You're scraped here.

297
00:18:07,497 --> 00:18:08,698
Does it hurt?

298
00:18:10,737 --> 00:18:11,938
Why did you come?

299
00:18:13,978 --> 00:18:14,777
Why did I come?

300
00:18:15,497 --> 00:18:16,497
So I couldn't come?

301
00:18:18,658 --> 00:18:20,057
You needed me. Of course I came.

302
00:18:20,777 --> 00:18:21,658
Don't be silly.

303
00:18:39,858 --> 00:18:41,577
I felt really embarrassed at first.

304
00:18:42,257 --> 00:18:43,698
When she grabbed me,

305
00:18:47,057 --> 00:18:49,297
everyone's stares felt like
they were eating me alive.

306
00:18:49,938 --> 00:18:53,017
I thought maybe it'd be better
if she just beat me to death.

307
00:18:55,537 --> 00:18:56,698
But when you showed up,

308
00:18:57,658 --> 00:18:59,817
I wasn't scared of anything anymore
as I saw you.

309
00:19:01,537 --> 00:19:04,297
Don't think I'll forgive you
just because you said all this.

310
00:19:05,698 --> 00:19:06,817
We're not back together yet.

311
00:19:13,618 --> 00:19:14,537
Crybaby.

312
00:19:18,698 --> 00:19:19,497
You wouldn't...

313
00:19:24,378 --> 00:19:25,138
Of course not.

314
00:19:32,497 --> 00:19:34,378
Aren't your feet cold without socks?

315
00:19:37,337 --> 00:19:37,837
Here.

316
00:19:40,378 --> 00:19:41,057
Gloves?

317
00:19:46,218 --> 00:19:46,858
They should fit.

318
00:19:50,898 --> 00:19:52,458
Try putting them on.

319
00:20:06,817 --> 00:20:07,317
Come on.

320
00:20:09,458 --> 00:20:10,337
Bai Shu?

321
00:20:10,497 --> 00:20:11,297
Long time no see.

322
00:20:12,418 --> 00:20:14,458
What are you doing? Turn around.

323
00:20:15,057 --> 00:20:15,898
Stop looking.

324
00:20:17,658 --> 00:20:19,378
Why not just tell him to close his eyes?

325
00:20:21,858 --> 00:20:22,418
Right.

326
00:20:23,097 --> 00:20:25,337
Do you think
my head was hit during the fight?

327
00:20:26,218 --> 00:20:27,257
I'm seriously dumbed down.

328
00:20:27,497 --> 00:20:29,618
Who hit you? What happened to you two?

329
00:20:29,777 --> 00:20:30,898
Got hit by an ugly monster.

330
00:20:32,737 --> 00:20:34,737
Then why did they
only hit Bai Shu and not you?

331
00:20:35,577 --> 00:20:37,138
Bai Shu, is it bad?

332
00:20:37,497 --> 00:20:38,938
It's fine. It doesn't hurt.

333
00:20:39,017 --> 00:20:40,097
What are you doing?

334
00:20:40,577 --> 00:20:41,432
Have some hot water.

335
00:20:42,097 --> 00:20:42,938
- Go inside.
- No.

336
00:20:42,938 --> 00:20:43,978
Turn around.

337
00:20:43,978 --> 00:20:46,057
I won't go back.
I want to stay with you.

338
00:20:46,337 --> 00:20:47,858
Then shut up, no talking.

339
00:20:48,777 --> 00:20:49,958
Turn around. Turn around.

340
00:20:50,418 --> 00:20:51,178
I won't talk.

341
00:20:51,378 --> 00:20:52,938
No talking, got it?

342
00:20:55,817 --> 00:20:56,458
Where's Mom?

343
00:20:59,297 --> 00:21:00,898
I'm talking to you. Where did Mom go?

344
00:21:03,618 --> 00:21:04,898
Didn't you say no talking?

345
00:21:05,938 --> 00:21:06,938
You can talk.

346
00:21:07,978 --> 00:21:10,968
Mom's on a night shift at the bathhouse.
She will be back tomorrow morning.

347
00:21:11,577 --> 00:21:13,138
Doesn't Ms. Ren work at the hospital?

348
00:21:13,817 --> 00:21:16,418
She still works there.
She just wants to earn more money.

349
00:21:17,017 --> 00:21:19,337
She gives scrubs at the bathhouse
when she's not working.

350
00:21:24,057 --> 00:21:26,378
Come on, you should take a shower.

351
00:21:30,057 --> 00:21:31,257
Can I help with anything?

352
00:21:31,257 --> 00:21:32,178
You bathe her?

353
00:21:34,337 --> 00:21:34,978
No.

354
00:21:35,138 --> 00:21:36,817
I'll show you
how to use the water heater.

355
00:21:38,057 --> 00:21:41,577
Xiaoming, I changed the sheets
and duvet cover. The bed is made too.

356
00:21:47,218 --> 00:21:48,378
Okay. Go to sleep.

357
00:21:50,057 --> 00:21:50,938
I'll take the couch.

358
00:22:02,017 --> 00:22:03,017
Why look at me?

359
00:22:08,858 --> 00:22:11,618
I'm not a mistress.
I didn't latch onto some rich guy.

360
00:22:13,378 --> 00:22:14,858
Nothing happened between us.

361
00:22:16,097 --> 00:22:18,057
Then why didn't you tell me that day?

362
00:22:19,297 --> 00:22:20,378
You didn't ask.

363
00:22:21,537 --> 00:22:22,698
You accused me straight away.

364
00:22:24,138 --> 00:22:24,898
So I was mad.

365
00:22:25,658 --> 00:22:27,138
You said you weren't at school.

366
00:22:28,138 --> 00:22:29,297
But you clearly were.

367
00:22:30,017 --> 00:22:32,337
And I saw you get out of a luxury car
with a guy.

368
00:22:34,737 --> 00:22:35,497
I was mad.

369
00:22:37,577 --> 00:22:41,378
That guy is Wang Hao.
I work for him as a translator.

370
00:22:41,978 --> 00:22:43,378
When I said I got some money,

371
00:22:44,577 --> 00:22:46,017
I was talking about my pay.

372
00:22:49,178 --> 00:22:50,378
I'm sorry.

373
00:22:51,658 --> 00:22:54,658
The whole world can doubt me,
but not you.

374
00:22:57,097 --> 00:22:58,337
So cringey. So annoying.

375
00:23:01,017 --> 00:23:02,537
You said I'm like my mom.

376
00:23:02,858 --> 00:23:03,858
How am I like her?

377
00:23:03,858 --> 00:23:05,017
I hate when people say that.

378
00:23:05,017 --> 00:23:05,577
You know that.

379
00:23:05,938 --> 00:23:08,938
I know. That's why I said it
on purpose to annoy you.

380
00:23:08,938 --> 00:23:09,438
Bad guy.

381
00:23:10,178 --> 00:23:10,737
You're bad.

382
00:23:10,858 --> 00:23:11,358
You're bad.

383
00:23:11,378 --> 00:23:12,658
- You're bad.
- You're bad.

384
00:23:15,737 --> 00:23:16,737
Even though we haven't

385
00:23:17,938 --> 00:23:18,938
talked for half a year

386
00:23:20,057 --> 00:23:21,080
and you didn't call me,

387
00:23:21,737 --> 00:23:22,938
I knew you thought about me.

388
00:23:25,057 --> 00:23:25,858
I did not.

389
00:23:26,577 --> 00:23:28,057
How did you know I worked in Qingzhou?

390
00:23:28,057 --> 00:23:29,737
Who told you? I never told you.

391
00:23:30,097 --> 00:23:31,017
You asked around, huh?

392
00:23:31,097 --> 00:23:32,497
You were thinking about me, right?

393
00:23:32,938 --> 00:23:33,458
Conceited.

394
00:23:33,777 --> 00:23:34,497
Stubborn.

395
00:23:34,817 --> 00:23:35,618
Conceited.

396
00:23:35,618 --> 00:23:37,057
So what if I'm conceited?

397
00:23:41,497 --> 00:23:42,777
How was your past half-year?

398
00:23:46,858 --> 00:23:48,698
I don't want to remember
what happened before.

399
00:23:49,777 --> 00:23:50,978
Can we not talk about it?

400
00:23:59,138 --> 00:24:00,497
I know you have a secret

401
00:24:01,737 --> 00:24:03,017
that you don't want to say.

402
00:24:04,017 --> 00:24:05,817
It's fine.
Double standards are okay for you.

403
00:24:06,537 --> 00:24:08,418
I can't have secrets from you,
but you can.

404
00:24:15,737 --> 00:24:17,898
Do you think
we'll lose contact again in the future?

405
00:24:19,658 --> 00:24:20,178
No, we won't.

406
00:24:21,017 --> 00:24:22,017
Then promise me.

407
00:24:22,658 --> 00:24:25,178
No matter what happens
between us from now on,

408
00:24:25,698 --> 00:24:27,458
you absolutely
can't lose contact with me.

409
00:24:31,057 --> 00:24:33,658
I don't believe what you say.

410
00:24:41,938 --> 00:24:44,938
Pinky swear, sealed forever,
a hundred years, no changes.

411
00:24:45,057 --> 00:24:46,232
Whoever breaks it is a dog.

412
00:25:04,698 --> 00:25:07,138
(Qidaohezi, 2023)
Uncle Haozi's real name is Wang Hao.

413
00:25:08,017 --> 00:25:11,777
He was the boss of La City's
Mistique Import & Export Trading Co.

414
00:25:12,218 --> 00:25:15,418
Now that company has been dissolved.

415
00:25:15,938 --> 00:25:18,017
And Wang Hao has immigrated
to Singapore.

416
00:25:18,698 --> 00:25:19,297
Captain Li,

417
00:25:20,138 --> 00:25:21,978
guess what year he left?

418
00:25:23,817 --> 00:25:26,978
Since you're asking like that,
it must be 2010.

419
00:25:27,497 --> 00:25:28,337
Captain Li.

420
00:25:29,658 --> 00:25:33,618
Now, turn to page 151,
second paragraph. Look here.

421
00:25:34,257 --> 00:25:37,978
That woman's eyes
are like those of a leopard.

422
00:25:38,257 --> 00:25:39,938
She lunged at Shu and Xiaoxi,

423
00:25:40,257 --> 00:25:42,698
cursing Shu as a homewrecker
and a seductress.

424
00:25:43,138 --> 00:25:45,257
Let me see. How did I miss this part?

425
00:25:45,737 --> 00:25:46,737
It's normal to miss this.

426
00:25:47,017 --> 00:25:48,577
I found it in the digital version.

427
00:25:49,057 --> 00:25:51,858
Throughout the novel, apart from
the Leopard and Graveyard chapter,

428
00:25:52,057 --> 00:25:54,858
this is the only place
where the word "leopard" appears.

429
00:25:55,378 --> 00:25:57,297
It felt like finding a needle
in a haystack.

430
00:25:58,497 --> 00:26:01,138
So the "leopard" here

431
00:26:01,777 --> 00:26:03,898
is Uncle Haozi's wife.

432
00:26:04,337 --> 00:26:06,297
Uncle Haozi's wife is named Zhou Na.

433
00:26:06,938 --> 00:26:08,257
She's 16 years younger than him.

434
00:26:10,938 --> 00:26:12,297
Huang Yue, stop writing.

435
00:26:12,577 --> 00:26:13,077
What's up?

436
00:26:13,777 --> 00:26:14,537
Come with me.

437
00:26:15,858 --> 00:26:17,218
We're paying Ge Wenjun a visit.

438
00:26:17,618 --> 00:26:18,378
Captain Li, we...

439
00:26:18,378 --> 00:26:19,057
Keep reading.

440
00:26:19,178 --> 00:26:19,777
Dig deeper.

441
00:26:20,057 --> 00:26:20,817
Yanzi, go for it.

442
00:26:23,138 --> 00:26:24,577
Let's read. More carefully.

443
00:26:29,577 --> 00:26:30,938
Do you know Wang Hao?

444
00:26:32,097 --> 00:26:33,577
Many people are named Wang Hao.

445
00:26:41,577 --> 00:26:42,938
In this novel,

446
00:26:43,618 --> 00:26:46,418
a mother called the police
late at night,

447
00:26:46,777 --> 00:26:49,537
claiming her daughter
was sexually assaulted.

448
00:26:50,737 --> 00:26:52,777
Does this plot sound familiar to you?

449
00:26:56,017 --> 00:26:58,178
I never read such cheap novels.

450
00:26:59,017 --> 00:27:01,297
Nor do I like
discussing pointless matters.

451
00:27:04,698 --> 00:27:05,777
A mother would

452
00:27:06,618 --> 00:27:08,218
do anything to protect her daughter,

453
00:27:09,497 --> 00:27:11,618
even at the cost of her own life.

454
00:27:13,618 --> 00:27:15,017
Calling the police is nothing.

455
00:27:16,618 --> 00:27:17,118
Okay.

456
00:27:22,898 --> 00:27:23,898
In 1972,

457
00:27:25,097 --> 00:27:28,777
you and a man named Wang Hao
were in the same production team.

458
00:27:29,017 --> 00:27:31,577
(Information about Wang Hao)
In 1989, Wang Hao

459
00:27:31,858 --> 00:27:34,737
worked as your driver
at your construction site.

460
00:27:39,017 --> 00:27:41,057
Wang Hao. Does that ring a bell now?

461
00:27:43,297 --> 00:27:44,777
What exactly are you trying to ask?

462
00:27:45,097 --> 00:27:47,297
Do you know Zhou Na, Wang Hao's wife?

463
00:27:54,337 --> 00:27:56,737
Right, many people
are named Zhou Na too.

464
00:27:58,658 --> 00:28:00,057
But the Zhou Na I'm referring to

465
00:28:00,378 --> 00:28:02,777
divorced Wang Hao in 2009.

466
00:28:03,497 --> 00:28:05,737
But after the divorce,
where did Zhou Na go?

467
00:28:06,337 --> 00:28:07,057
Do you know?

468
00:28:07,658 --> 00:28:10,138
You just said they were divorced.

469
00:28:10,618 --> 00:28:13,257
A divorced woman is free.

470
00:28:13,817 --> 00:28:15,458
She can go wherever she wants.

471
00:28:22,577 --> 00:28:24,178
The deceased is very likely Zhou Na.

472
00:28:25,257 --> 00:28:26,297
How did you know, Ma'am?

473
00:28:26,858 --> 00:28:30,938
I didn't come here to get information
about Zhou Na from Ge Wenjun,

474
00:28:31,097 --> 00:28:32,257
but to observe her attitude.

475
00:28:33,017 --> 00:28:35,178
Was there a problem with her attitude?

476
00:28:35,777 --> 00:28:37,737
The novel portrayed her so horribly,

477
00:28:37,978 --> 00:28:39,497
yet she didn't offer much explanation.

478
00:28:40,297 --> 00:28:42,938
She'd rather take the blame
for falsely accusing Wang Hao

479
00:28:42,938 --> 00:28:44,537
than talk to us more about Zhou Na.

480
00:28:45,057 --> 00:28:47,418
Don't you find it quite strange?

481
00:28:48,618 --> 00:28:50,938
Yeah, that's why you're our master.

482
00:28:50,938 --> 00:28:52,257
How come I didn't think of that?

483
00:28:52,898 --> 00:28:53,737
Keep learning.

484
00:28:54,297 --> 00:28:55,057
Got it.

485
00:28:56,537 --> 00:28:57,618
For this case,

486
00:28:59,297 --> 00:29:01,337
we just dealt with Zhou Yun.

487
00:29:07,817 --> 00:29:09,138
(Zhou Na)
And now comes

488
00:29:09,858 --> 00:29:10,458
Zhou Na.

489
00:29:12,737 --> 00:29:15,017
Shun, have you reached Wang Hao?

490
00:29:15,938 --> 00:29:17,057
We've contacted Wang Hao.

491
00:29:17,337 --> 00:29:19,698
He said he can find time
to come back to Qidaohezi soon

492
00:29:20,057 --> 00:29:20,817
to work with us.

493
00:29:21,458 --> 00:29:22,257
Keep pushing him.

494
00:29:23,178 --> 00:29:24,337
According to Hukou info,

495
00:29:24,577 --> 00:29:26,232
Zhou Na was
originally from Macau, China.

496
00:29:26,537 --> 00:29:29,257
She illegally went abroad to work
in an underground casino abroad.

497
00:29:29,458 --> 00:29:31,297
After she divorced Wang Hao in 2009,

498
00:29:31,537 --> 00:29:33,658
no one knew
if she was still in the country.

499
00:29:34,178 --> 00:29:37,097
This really makes
our investigation difficult, guys.

500
00:29:38,777 --> 00:29:39,378
Spread out.

501
00:29:40,017 --> 00:29:40,938
Through all channels,

502
00:29:43,017 --> 00:29:43,898
find this leopard.

503
00:29:44,337 --> 00:29:47,257
Ma'am, should we
keep reading this novel?

504
00:29:47,418 --> 00:29:48,497
If we keep reading,

505
00:29:48,497 --> 00:29:49,777
it's all about dating.

506
00:29:50,577 --> 00:29:51,898
So we won't read about dating?

507
00:29:52,537 --> 00:29:53,577
We absolutely must read.

508
00:29:54,418 --> 00:29:54,978
Remember,

509
00:29:55,378 --> 00:29:56,777
get the details and find the clues.

510
00:29:57,858 --> 00:30:00,297
Captain Li, it's not all about dating.

511
00:30:01,017 --> 00:30:04,017
I think the character Zhang Fang
is strange in the novel.

512
00:30:04,618 --> 00:30:05,297
Why is that?

513
00:30:05,817 --> 00:30:07,497
He is a main character.

514
00:30:07,817 --> 00:30:10,497
(Zhang Fang)
He's an important one among the four.

515
00:30:11,577 --> 00:30:15,418
But the author uniquely
didn't write his ending.

516
00:30:20,658 --> 00:30:22,057
Zhang Fang.

517
00:30:22,802 --> 00:30:27,387
(La City Normal College, 2008)

518
00:30:31,922 --> 00:30:33,362
(Dorm 8)

519
00:30:38,257 --> 00:30:39,097
What are you doing?

520
00:30:41,017 --> 00:30:41,898
Who are you?

521
00:30:42,698 --> 00:30:43,978
Zhang Fang, Bai Shu's classmate.

522
00:30:43,978 --> 00:30:44,938
Why are you shouting?

523
00:30:50,218 --> 00:30:51,218
Give the suitcase back.

524
00:30:51,898 --> 00:30:53,097
Or I'll call security.

525
00:30:54,257 --> 00:30:55,737
You promised to let Bai Shu board.

526
00:30:56,138 --> 00:30:57,858
What's this?
Why are you moving her things?

527
00:31:07,017 --> 00:31:08,057
Bai Shu dropped out.

528
00:31:09,257 --> 00:31:09,978
Why?

529
00:31:11,138 --> 00:31:11,978
Was it you again?

530
00:31:12,218 --> 00:31:13,138
Why are you shouting?

531
00:31:13,537 --> 00:31:14,978
Aren't you embarrassed for Bai Shu?

532
00:31:23,138 --> 00:31:25,218
It seems you don't know what happened.

533
00:31:32,898 --> 00:31:35,257
Zhang Fang, who are you angry with?

534
00:31:35,597 --> 00:31:36,097
Fine.

535
00:31:36,097 --> 00:31:36,658
That's enough.

536
00:31:36,698 --> 00:31:37,198
Okay, fine.

537
00:31:37,497 --> 00:31:38,257
Stop drinking.

538
00:31:39,898 --> 00:31:42,257
Everyone, quiet.
I have something serious to say.

539
00:31:42,577 --> 00:31:43,257
Here's the thing.

540
00:31:44,017 --> 00:31:45,017
With the words here,

541
00:31:46,618 --> 00:31:48,418
"Friendship Forever",

542
00:31:49,297 --> 00:31:51,858
we are the VIPs of this table.

543
00:31:53,178 --> 00:31:55,458
(Braised pork, boiled pork, pork stew)
This table will never disappear.

